text: Buckingham Hockey Club is a field hockey club based at Stowe School near Buckingham. The club also play fixtures at Akeley Wood School in Buckingham and Buckingham Town Cricket Club. The Women's 1st Team play in the Investec Women's Hockey League Premier Division and the Men's team who play in the South Hockey League (Middx, Berks, Bucks & Oxon - Division 3). ==Players== ===Women's First Team Squad 2020-21 Season === (captain) http://www.englandhockey.co.uk/page_noside.asp?section=2342§ionTitle;=Fixtures%2C+Results+%26+Standings ==Major Honours== * 2015-16 Women's Cup Runner-Up ==References== Category:English field hockey clubs
